summary: Skills are vital for personal and professional growth, enabling individuals to leverage strengths, address weaknesses, and drive innovation. This collection features a course on engineering breakthroughs, fostering unique capabilities, resilience, and effective communication in startups through SWOT analysis and critical asks.
excerpt: Discover personal strengths and embrace weaknesses in the Engineer Breakthroughs course. Learn to conduct SWOT analysis, formulate critical asks, and drive innovation in startups for strategic growth.
